 Tak]], Tez and [[Delhi Aaj Tak]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiantelevision.com/headlines/y2k4/nov/nov75.htm|title=Alok Verma to head TV Today spl. projects|date=8 November 2004|publisher=}}</ref> was brought in as the Executive Producer to successfully launch TV Today group's foray into the English news channel category.<ref>{{cite news|title=Aaj Tak English channel may launch in 10 days|url=http://www.indiantelevision.com/old-html/headlines/y2k3/feb/feb151.htm|accessdate=3 April 2017|work=Indian Television|date=24 February 2003}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=TV Today's Delhi Aaj Tak likely to launch mid-May |url=http://www.indiantelevision.com/node/23101 |publisher=Indian Television |accessdate=3 April 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207233838/http://www.indiantelevision.com/node/23101 |archivedate=7 February 2016 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref> Media watchers flagged the channel for unethical use of footage in September 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehoot.org/media-watch/media-practice/unethical-use-of-unrelated-videos-8912|title=Unethical use of  unrelated videos|publisher=}}</ref> and sexist content.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehoot.org/media-watch-briefs/india-today-s-offensive-video-8205|title=India Today's offensive video|publisher=}}</ref>\n\n== Associated journalists==\n\n* [[Rahul Kanwal]] - News Director\n* [[Rajdeep Sardesai]] - Consulting Editor\n* [[Gaurav C Sawant]] - Executive Editor\n* [[Shiv Aroor]] - Consulting Editor\n* [[Chaiti Narula]] - Deputy Editor\n\nAnchors include [[Preeti Choudhry]], Sushant Mehta, [[Shiv Aroor]], Gaurav Sawant, Ankit Tyagi, [[Chaiti Narula]].\n\n== Awards==\n* Exchange4media News Broadcasting Awards 2015<ref>{{cite web|title=TV Today Network wins big at ENBA 2015|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/enba-2015-india-today-television-wins-big/1/595343.html|accessdate=3 April 2017}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n* ''[[India Today]]''\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n